  "original_title": "\u0dad\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0dbb\u0ddd\u0daf \u0dbb\u0dd2\u0dba\u0d9a\u0da7 \u0dc3\u0dad\u0dd2\u0dba\u0d9a\u0da7 \u0dbd\u0dd3\u0da7\u0dbb\u0dca 30\u0d9a\u0dca \u0d85\u0dc0\u0dc1\u0dca\u200d\u0dba\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A three-wheeler needs 30 liters per week",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Mr. Lalith Dharmasekara, President of All Ceylon Tricycle Drivers Trade Union, told 'Lankadeepa' that the government is requested to provide 30 liters of petrol per week to three-wheelers engaged in public transport.",
        "Mr. Dharmasekera said that 5 liters of petrol per week is absolutely not enough for three-wheeler drivers who work as a means of public transport and also stated that he refuses to register the three-wheelers used in public transport to be registered with the police.",
        "Mr. Dharmasekara said that it is not reasonable to demand that the toll meters be made mandatory at this time when the three-wheeler drivers are in difficulty. Mr. Dharmasekara said that it should be made mandatory to display the toll meters as 100 rupees for the first kilometer and 90 rupees for the second kilometer.",
        "Just like regulating other public transport services, the National Transport Commission should authorize and start regulating three-wheelers from this special time, otherwise lakhs of people who are employed in three-wheelers will fall on the road.",
        "Mr. Dharmasekara also added that 5 liters per week can be given to the three-wheelers that are used privately using the normal method.",
        "It also said that there is technology to easily monitor whether the three-wheelers are actually engaged in transport."
      ],
